Text.SourceString: Good morning, baby! Still got sand between my toes from our beach wedding yesterday.//Feels like some wild dream, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: Good morning, baby! Still got sand between my toes from our beach wedding yesterday.//Feels like some wild dream, huh?

Text.SourceString: And your outfit, oof! Just so you know, I've been mentally strutting around all morning thinking, "Yeah, I married THAT." You were a knockout.
Text.LocalizedString: And your outfit, oof! Just so you know, I've been mentally strutting around all morning thinking, "Yeah, I married THAT." You were a knockout.

Text.SourceString: Gah, setting up that home gym was a workout itself, huh?//<portrait=happy>Maybe we should call this our rest week already. Feels like we've done a month's worth of lifting!
Text.LocalizedString: Gah, setting up that home gym was a workout itself, huh?//<portrait=happy>Maybe we should call this our rest week already. Feels like we've done a month's worth of lifting!

Text.SourceString: I sprinted to the hot spring and back this morning. You wouldn't believe how beautiful the route is from our farm.//Postcard view, baby...yeah!
Text.LocalizedString: I sprinted to the hot spring and back this morning. You wouldn't believe how beautiful the route is from our farm.//Postcard view, baby...yeah!

Text.SourceString: Morning, babe! Made a breakfast for you. Gotta make sure you're not running on empty.
Text.LocalizedString: Morning, babe! Made a breakfast for you. Gotta make sure you're not running on empty.

Text.SourceString: I made you something after my workout this morning!//Dig in, babe! Keep that belly happy and full.
Text.LocalizedString: I made you something after my workout this morning!//Dig in, babe! Keep that belly happy and full.

Text.SourceString: It's raining again. Wanna race banana leaves boat down the stream? Winner gets a kiss!
Text.LocalizedString: It's raining again. Wanna race banana leaves boat down the stream? Winner gets a kiss!

Text.SourceString: Life is full of beautiful surprises, isn't it, <PlayerName>$player</>?//<portrait=blushing>I never knew I could feel this way about someone. You truly have my heart.
Text.LocalizedString: Life is full of beautiful surprises, isn't it, <PlayerName>$player</>?//<portrait=blushing>I never knew I could feel this way about someone. You truly have my heart.

Text.SourceString: So, any exciting plans for the day?
Text.LocalizedString: So, any exciting plans for the day?

Text.SourceString: Do we have any plans this Summer, babe? I know there's a beach clean-up... Am I forgetting anything?
Text.LocalizedString: Do we have any plans this Summer, babe? I know there's a beach clean-up... Am I forgetting anything?

Text.SourceString: How was your day today, <PlayerName>$Player</>? Everything running smoothly on the farm?
Text.LocalizedString: How was your day today, <PlayerName>$Player</>? Everything running smoothly on the farm?

Text.SourceString: Babe, can you check the kitchen later? There were some noises last night...//Could be a leak, or maybe...just maybe, we've got ghosts...I don't know.
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, can you check the kitchen later? There were some noises last night...//Could be a leak, or maybe...just maybe, we've got ghosts...I don't know.

Text.SourceString: Last night I heard a creak coming from the window. What do you think it is?//It's probably just the wind... I don't know, should I be scared? 'Cause I already am.
Text.LocalizedString: Last night I heard a creak coming from the window. What do you think it is?//It's probably just the wind... I don't know, should I be scared? 'Cause I already am.

Text.SourceString: I love this house... It's so peaceful out here.
Text.LocalizedString: I love this house... It's so peaceful out here.

Text.SourceString: I'm gonna grab some fruits and bring them over to <NPCName>Takeba</> later.//I might stop by Sam's too. Do you need anything?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm gonna grab some fruits and bring them over to <NPCName>Takeba</> later.//I might stop by Sam's too. Do you need anything?

Text.SourceString: My hair's getting long... I could use a shave on the side to freshen things up.//<portrait=sad>Babe, could you book that appointment for me? I really don't feel like it... <NPCName>Erika</> talks quite a bit
Text.LocalizedString: My hair's getting long... I could use a shave on the side to freshen things up.//<portrait=sad>Babe, could you book that appointment for me? I really don't feel like it... <NPCName>Erika</> talks quite a bit

Text.SourceString: It's so hard to get dirt stains out of spandex, I swear. I've tried everything...and <Italic>nothing</> seems to work sometimes.
Text.LocalizedString: It's so hard to get dirt stains out of spandex, I swear. I've tried everything...and <Italic>nothing</> seems to work sometimes.

Text.SourceString: I should just wear dark workout clothes.
Text.LocalizedString: I should just wear dark workout clothes.

Text.SourceString: Babe, we're off to the Animal Festival tomorrow, yeah?//<portrait=determined>Oh gosh! I can't wait to take a spin on that bull again.
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, we're off to the Animal Festival tomorrow, yeah?//<portrait=determined>Oh gosh! I can't wait to take a spin on that bull again.

Text.SourceString: What do you think is a good time to head out for the New Year's Eve party? We better not be late, babe.//<portrait=annoyed>You know how <NPCName>Scott</> is, always hogging the amuse-bouche. It's all gonna be gone if we're even a minute late!
Text.LocalizedString: What do you think is a good time to head out for the New Year's Eve party? We better not be late, babe.//<portrait=annoyed>You know how <NPCName>Scott</> is, always hogging the amuse-bouche. It's all gonna be gone if we're even a minute late!

Text.SourceString: So pumped for the boat ride tomorrow. That frog boat is the cutest thing ever.//We gotta get one of those, put it right in our pond!
Text.LocalizedString: So pumped for the boat ride tomorrow. That frog boat is the cutest thing ever.//We gotta get one of those, put it right in our pond!

Text.SourceString: Babe, if you're tryna dive, you can't do it from here. You gotta go there.//Go to the inn, then go south. You can dive there.
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, if you're tryna dive, you can't do it from here. You gotta go there.//Go to the inn, then go south. You can dive there.

Text.SourceString: I don't make the rules around here...you know that. If that were up to me, I'd let you dive...I'd let you do whatever you want here.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't make the rules around here...you know that. If that were up to me, I'd let you dive...I'd let you do whatever you want here.

Text.SourceString: My job’s not just a day at the beach. I have to be on the lookout all the time.//It only takes a split second for somebody to get into trouble in the water.
Text.LocalizedString: My job’s not just a day at the beach. I have to be on the lookout all the time.//It only takes a split second for somebody to get into trouble in the water.

Text.SourceString: And those riptides are no joke!//People think they’re good swimmers, but the waves will pull you under in a split second.
Text.LocalizedString: And those riptides are no joke!//People think they’re good swimmers, but the waves will pull you under in a split second.

Text.SourceString: Didn’t mean to freak you out! It’s calm most of the time. But when a lifeguard tells you to stay close to shore, pay attention.//<portrait=determined>We’re just looking out for you.
Text.LocalizedString: Didn’t mean to freak you out! It’s calm most of the time. But when a lifeguard tells you to stay close to shore, pay attention.//<portrait=determined>We’re just looking out for you.

Text.SourceString: I’m <Italic>starving</>.//Training always makes me hungry.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m <Italic>starving</>.//Training always makes me hungry.

Text.SourceString: Do you have any food with you? Pizza? Pasta? Oh, ramen?!//<portrait=happy>I would kill for some ramen right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you have any food with you? Pizza? Pasta? Oh, ramen?!//<portrait=happy>I would kill for some ramen right now.

Text.SourceString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!

Text.SourceString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.
Text.LocalizedString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.

Text.SourceString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!

Text.SourceString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.
Text.LocalizedString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.

Text.SourceString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!

Text.SourceString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.
Text.LocalizedString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.

Text.SourceString: The hot spring is really good for sore muscles. Nothing beats a hot soak after a hard workout.
Text.LocalizedString: The hot spring is really good for sore muscles. Nothing beats a hot soak after a hard workout.

Text.SourceString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!
Text.LocalizedString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!

Text.SourceString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!
Text.LocalizedString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!

Text.SourceString: Check out my new sneakers! They give me extra spring in my toes. Perfect for volleyball.
Text.LocalizedString: Check out my new sneakers! They give me extra spring in my toes. Perfect for volleyball.

Text.SourceString: I paid way too much for these shoes. Hopefully, they’re going to up my game.
Text.LocalizedString: I paid way too much for these shoes. Hopefully, they’re going to up my game.

Text.SourceString: There's this pink tree next to the observatory... Yeah, the big cherry tree right in the middle of the hot spring.
Text.LocalizedString: There's this pink tree next to the observatory... Yeah, the big cherry tree right in the middle of the hot spring.

Text.SourceString: It's...pretty, I guess. But those damn petals always clog up the drain in the observatory. Such a pain to clean.
Text.LocalizedString: It's...pretty, I guess. But those damn petals always clog up the drain in the observatory. Such a pain to clean.

Text.SourceString: Watch out for jellyfish on the beach.//Don’t get stung.
Text.LocalizedString: Watch out for jellyfish on the beach.//Don’t get stung.

Text.SourceString: Oof, the beach is gross today. Smells like dead fish.
Text.LocalizedString: Oof, the beach is gross today. Smells like dead fish.

Text.SourceString: I think it’s just seaweed that washed up, but still. Ugh.
Text.LocalizedString: I think it’s just seaweed that washed up, but still. Ugh.

Text.SourceString: This storm is wild! The beach is going to be a mess tomorrow.//All sorts of trash and debris washes up after weather like this.
Text.LocalizedString: This storm is wild! The beach is going to be a mess tomorrow.//All sorts of trash and debris washes up after weather like this.

Text.SourceString: This storm is wild! The beach is going to be a mess tomorrow.//All sorts of trash and debris washes up after weather like this.
Text.LocalizedString: This storm is wild! The beach is going to be a mess tomorrow.//All sorts of trash and debris washes up after weather like this.

Text.SourceString: This storm is wild! Watch out.
Text.LocalizedString: This storm is wild! Watch out.

Text.SourceString: This storm is wild! Watch out.
Text.LocalizedString: This storm is wild! Watch out.

Text.SourceString: It’s almost the end of the year already. Fast, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: It’s almost the end of the year already. Fast, huh?

Text.SourceString: I might take a class online to learn something new.//Not right now. I’m way too busy. But maybe this Winter, when it’s too cold for volleyball.
Text.LocalizedString: I might take a class online to learn something new.//Not right now. I’m way too busy. But maybe this Winter, when it’s too cold for volleyball.

Text.SourceString: Winter’s almost here.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter’s almost here.

Text.SourceString: I still run to the beach, but the snow slows me down! Bah!//And when it’s icy, forget it. Trying to run on ice is a sure way to break a bone.
Text.LocalizedString: I still run to the beach, but the snow slows me down! Bah!//And when it’s icy, forget it. Trying to run on ice is a sure way to break a bone.

Text.SourceString: The hot spring sounds good right now.
Text.LocalizedString: The hot spring sounds good right now.

Text.SourceString: I’m so itchy today! I’ve got bug bites all over my legs.//The bugs are out in force lately. Great!
Text.LocalizedString: I’m so itchy today! I’ve got bug bites all over my legs.//The bugs are out in force lately. Great!

Text.SourceString: I think we should get one of those mosquito nets and turn it into clothing. It could come in handy.//<portrait=determined>Oh, come on! I'll wear it if you wear it. Yeah?
Text.LocalizedString: I think we should get one of those mosquito nets and turn it into clothing. It could come in handy.//<portrait=determined>Oh, come on! I'll wear it if you wear it. Yeah?

Text.SourceString: The weather is warming up.//If I dressed any warmer, I’d sweat <Italic>buckets</>.
Text.LocalizedString: The weather is warming up.//If I dressed any warmer, I’d sweat <Italic>buckets</>.

Text.SourceString: It’s Spring, baby! Time to hit the volleyball court and work off my Winter blues!
Text.LocalizedString: It’s Spring, baby! Time to hit the volleyball court and work off my Winter blues!

Text.SourceString: I managed to stay in pretty good shape over Winter, but I feel a little off my game, you know?//<portrait=determined>I’m itching to get in a good workout.
Text.LocalizedString: I managed to stay in pretty good shape over Winter, but I feel a little off my game, you know?//<portrait=determined>I’m itching to get in a good workout.

Text.SourceString: You know the plastic rings six-packs come in?//<portrait=sad>They can kill sea life if they end up in the ocean. It’s so sad.//We should make a public service announcement about that.
Text.LocalizedString: You know the plastic rings six-packs come in?//<portrait=sad>They can kill sea life if they end up in the ocean. It’s so sad.//We should make a public service announcement about that.

Text.SourceString: I already talked to the mayor, but he shot down the idea...even when I offered to be the face of it.//Ah, baby, can you imagine? Your wife, a big screen star? Are you ready for that?! Hah!
Text.LocalizedString: I already talked to the mayor, but he shot down the idea...even when I offered to be the face of it.//Ah, baby, can you imagine? Your wife, a big screen star? Are you ready for that?! Hah!

Text.SourceString: I don’t like staying indoors too long, sitting behind a desk. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t like staying indoors too long, sitting behind a desk. Bah!

Text.SourceString: The human body was built to move.
Text.LocalizedString: The human body was built to move.

Text.SourceString: There’s usually an influx of people visiting the beach in Summer.//I get it. Summer, beach. Yeah, whatever.
Text.LocalizedString: There’s usually an influx of people visiting the beach in Summer.//I get it. Summer, beach. Yeah, whatever.

Text.SourceString: I’m seeing more and more people busting out the swimwear.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m seeing more and more people busting out the swimwear.

Text.SourceString: But hey, my baby has nothing to worry about. My eyes are locked on you, and only you.
Text.LocalizedString: But hey, my baby has nothing to worry about. My eyes are locked on you, and only you.

Text.SourceString: Never buying from White Flamingo again.//Got myself a brand new pair of sunnies, and... The very first wear, and they snap. Dang it!
Text.LocalizedString: Never buying from White Flamingo again.//Got myself a brand new pair of sunnies, and... The very first wear, and they snap. Dang it!

Text.SourceString: Okay, yeah... I accidentally sat on them, but come on, babe, I sat on them just <Italic>once</>. So frustrating!
Text.LocalizedString: Okay, yeah... I accidentally sat on them, but come on, babe, I sat on them just <Italic>once</>. So frustrating!

Text.SourceString: Stargazing is cool.//I didn't think much of it at first, but when I used to live at the observatory, it kinda grew on me.
Text.LocalizedString: Stargazing is cool.//I didn't think much of it at first, but when I used to live at the observatory, it kinda grew on me.

Text.SourceString: I always see <NPCName>Zoe</> and her family playing volleyball at the beach. I don't want to bother them, but if <NPCName>Zoe</>'s serious about playing, maybe I could take her under my wing.
Text.LocalizedString: I always see <NPCName>Zoe</> and her family playing volleyball at the beach. I don't want to bother them, but if <NPCName>Zoe</>'s serious about playing, maybe I could take her under my wing.

Text.SourceString: The girl's got skills, no doubt!
Text.LocalizedString: The girl's got skills, no doubt!

Text.SourceString: I was gonna get in some volleyball time, but it’s just too wet out there. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: I was gonna get in some volleyball time, but it’s just too wet out there. Bah!

Text.SourceString: Wanna cuddle instead?
Text.LocalizedString: Wanna cuddle instead?

Text.SourceString: It really rains the whole day, doesn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: It really rains the whole day, doesn’t it?

Text.SourceString: It really storms the whole day, doesn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: It really storms the whole day, doesn’t it?

Text.SourceString: I was gonna get in some volleyball time, but it’s just too wet out there. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: I was gonna get in some volleyball time, but it’s just too wet out there. Bah!

Text.SourceString: Wanna cuddle instead?
Text.LocalizedString: Wanna cuddle instead?

Text.SourceString: It’s gonna snow the whole day today. I just <Italic>know</> it.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s gonna snow the whole day today. I just <Italic>know</> it.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Zarah</> was using a metal detector down on the beach the other day, and she found a gold coin.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Zarah</> was using a metal detector down on the beach the other day, and she found a gold coin.

Text.SourceString: You think there might be more?//I should invest in a metal detector.
Text.LocalizedString: You think there might be more?//I should invest in a metal detector.

Text.SourceString: Found a pearl on the beach the other day. Not yours, is it?
Text.LocalizedString: Found a pearl on the beach the other day. Not yours, is it?

Text.SourceString: Sports teach humility. I like that.//Sometimes we win and sometimes we lose.
Text.LocalizedString: Sports teach humility. I like that.//Sometimes we win and sometimes we lose.

Text.SourceString: So what if you lose? Gotta face it and try again tomorrow.//It’s not the end of the world.
Text.LocalizedString: So what if you lose? Gotta face it and try again tomorrow.//It’s not the end of the world.

Text.SourceString: I used to swim a lot when I was a kid, but it didn’t grab me. Not competitive enough, I think.
Text.LocalizedString: I used to swim a lot when I was a kid, but it didn’t grab me. Not competitive enough, I think.

Text.SourceString: I like playing sports where there are winners and losers.
Text.LocalizedString: I like playing sports where there are winners and losers.

Text.SourceString: Apples are in season, no? Are we planning to plant some on our farm?
Text.LocalizedString: Apples are in season, no? Are we planning to plant some on our farm?

Text.SourceString: What’s with the giant chicken they have at the Harvest Festival, huh? So weird!//<portrait=determined>I know what I'm getting you for our anniversary. Heh!
Text.LocalizedString: What’s with the giant chicken they have at the Harvest Festival, huh? So weird!//<portrait=determined>I know what I'm getting you for our anniversary. Heh!

Text.SourceString: I cleaned the leaves in front of the bathhouse yesterday, and they’re already piling up again.
Text.LocalizedString: I cleaned the leaves in front of the bathhouse yesterday, and they’re already piling up again.

Text.SourceString: Need to find <NpcName>Wakuu</>. It’s his turn to clear the path for <NpcName>Takeba</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Need to find <NpcName>Wakuu</>. It’s his turn to clear the path for <NpcName>Takeba</>.

Text.SourceString: It’s freezing today.//Wanna do a few jumping jacks with me, babe? It'll get us toasty warm. Try it.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s freezing today.//Wanna do a few jumping jacks with me, babe? It'll get us toasty warm. Try it.

Text.SourceString: Ugh, this dry air is such a buzzkill! We need to hydrate...yeah, that's it.
Text.LocalizedString: Ugh, this dry air is such a buzzkill! We need to hydrate...yeah, that's it.

Text.SourceString: One of those giant animal suits from White Flamingo would be nice.//<portrait=determined>Nice and toasty inside.
Text.LocalizedString: One of those giant animal suits from White Flamingo would be nice.//<portrait=determined>Nice and toasty inside.

Text.SourceString: Are you doing one of those New Year’s resolution things?//<portrait=determined>Mine is the same every year. Get better at life.
Text.LocalizedString: Are you doing one of those New Year’s resolution things?//<portrait=determined>Mine is the same every year. Get better at life.

Text.SourceString: I've been swimming for ages, but you know what I secretly wish? More diving adventures!
Text.LocalizedString: I've been swimming for ages, but you know what I secretly wish? More diving adventures!

Text.SourceString: Maybe I should train to be a deep-sea diver, and then we can have some epic quality time exploring the ocean together. Who knows?
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I should train to be a deep-sea diver, and then we can have some epic quality time exploring the ocean together. Who knows?

Text.SourceString: Up for a game?
Text.LocalizedString: Up for a game?

Text.SourceString: Might stop by the Beach Shack later, pick up some coconuts. I’m kinda in the mood for one.//Do we need anything for the house, babe? I'll get it at the same time.
Text.LocalizedString: Might stop by the Beach Shack later, pick up some coconuts. I’m kinda in the mood for one.//Do we need anything for the house, babe? I'll get it at the same time.

Text.SourceString: Well, actually...if you go to Fishensips, I could use some gnocchi for dinner. Hehe! Pretty please?
Text.LocalizedString: Well, actually...if you go to Fishensips, I could use some gnocchi for dinner. Hehe! Pretty please?

Text.SourceString: I like playing volleyball with <NPCName>Aaliyah</>.//We both play hard, you know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: I like playing volleyball with <NPCName>Aaliyah</>.//We both play hard, you know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: Gosh, I love <NPCName>Taco</>...he's such a floofball.
Text.LocalizedString: Gosh, I love <NPCName>Taco</>...he's such a floofball.

Text.SourceString: This one time, I saw <NPCName>Taco</> swimming in the fountain. Yeah, the one in front of the general store.//<portrait=happy>What a funny little dude.
Text.LocalizedString: This one time, I saw <NPCName>Taco</> swimming in the fountain. Yeah, the one in front of the general store.//<portrait=happy>What a funny little dude.

Text.SourceString: Should we dance, babe? Or are you here to eat?
Text.LocalizedString: Should we dance, babe? Or are you here to eat?

Text.SourceString: Frank's pesto pasta is so good! You should order that.//If you have any leftovers, please don't throw them out. Just pop them in the fridge, and I'll eat them later.
Text.LocalizedString: Frank's pesto pasta is so good! You should order that.//If you have any leftovers, please don't throw them out. Just pop them in the fridge, and I'll eat them later.

Text.SourceString: I feel dizzy… My head…//Whoaaaaa… I might’ve caught something.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel dizzy… My head…//Whoaaaaa… I might’ve caught something.

Text.SourceString: I really don't feel like going to the clinic. I know <NPCName>Yuri</> is just going to tell me to rest. Ugh.//I don't wanna rest...
Text.LocalizedString: I really don't feel like going to the clinic. I know <NPCName>Yuri</> is just going to tell me to rest. Ugh.//I don't wanna rest...

Text.SourceString: Hmm… Should I get my flu shot now? Kinda don’t wanna go to the clinic.//Not a fan of clinics or hospitals. That’s where <Italic>sick</> people go, you know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm… Should I get my flu shot now? Kinda don’t wanna go to the clinic.//Not a fan of clinics or hospitals. That’s where <Italic>sick</> people go, you know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: I’m sure the one in town is cleaner than my room right now, but who knows what kind of germs or viruses are in there? *shivers*
Text.LocalizedString: I’m sure the one in town is cleaner than my room right now, but who knows what kind of germs or viruses are in there? *shivers*

Text.SourceString: I’m gonna have to skip the beach today.//<portrait=determined>Wanna see who can balance the most chips on their forehead? Winner gets kisses.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m gonna have to skip the beach today.//<portrait=determined>Wanna see who can balance the most chips on their forehead? Winner gets kisses.

Text.SourceString: Or do you wanna skip the formality and just give me kisses now?
Text.LocalizedString: Or do you wanna skip the formality and just give me kisses now?

Text.SourceString: I can’t believe how much weight I’ve been able to lift lately.//I’m really sore, though.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t believe how much weight I’ve been able to lift lately.//I’m really sore, though.

Text.SourceString: Dang, I forgot my water bottle again. I swear, my mind’s in the clouds today.//<portrait=annoyed>At least I still have my head on my shoulders, or I’d probably lose it too!
Text.LocalizedString: Dang, I forgot my water bottle again. I swear, my mind’s in the clouds today.//<portrait=annoyed>At least I still have my head on my shoulders, or I’d probably lose it too!

Text.SourceString: I think I pulled a muscle in my leg during practice the other day.//I’m going to have to sit out for a little while.
Text.LocalizedString: I think I pulled a muscle in my leg during practice the other day.//I’m going to have to sit out for a little while.

Text.SourceString: I’m hyped for the Cherry Blossom Festival next week. The food is always next level.//<portrait=normal>What are we bringing to the potluck, babe?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m hyped for the Cherry Blossom Festival next week. The food is always next level.//<portrait=normal>What are we bringing to the potluck, babe?

Text.SourceString: I gotta clean my place next week. It’s a total disaster.//<portrait=concerned>Also, I’m missing a pair of shorts.
Text.LocalizedString: I gotta clean my place next week. It’s a total disaster.//<portrait=concerned>Also, I’m missing a pair of shorts.

Text.SourceString: This year is zooming by <Italic>fast</>!//It feels like we just celebrated New Year’s yesterday.
Text.LocalizedString: This year is zooming by <Italic>fast</>!//It feels like we just celebrated New Year’s yesterday.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Aaliyah</> can throw stones so far out into the sea. I need to ask her to teach me how to do it.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Aaliyah</> can throw stones so far out into the sea. I need to ask her to teach me how to do it.

Text.SourceString: Dang, your smile is killer!
Text.LocalizedString: Dang, your smile is killer!

Text.SourceString: It’s infectious. I can’t help but smile when I’m around you.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s infectious. I can’t help but smile when I’m around you.

Text.SourceString: You look hot in that.
Text.LocalizedString: You look hot in that.

Text.SourceString: I can't believe you're mine. I'm so lucky.
Text.LocalizedString: I can't believe you're mine. I'm so lucky.

Text.SourceString: Where did you get that outfit, babe? You look great!
Text.LocalizedString: Where did you get that outfit, babe? You look great!

Text.SourceString: Babe... I just want to say that you're an amazing listener.//Whenever I talk to you, I truly feel heard and understood. It means the world to me.
Text.LocalizedString: Babe... I just want to say that you're an amazing listener.//Whenever I talk to you, I truly feel heard and understood. It means the world to me.

Text.SourceString: I love you, <PlayerName>$Player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I love you, <PlayerName>$Player</>.

Text.SourceString: Winter makes me appreciate the warmer weather even more.//Bring on the Summer sun, baby!
Text.LocalizedString: Winter makes me appreciate the warmer weather even more.//Bring on the Summer sun, baby!

Text.SourceString: I always feel like a real adult when I shovel snow.//<portrait=happy>Like, look at me being a responsible homeowner and stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: I always feel like a real adult when I shovel snow.//<portrait=happy>Like, look at me being a responsible homeowner and stuff.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Takeba</> takes great care of the bathhouse. We should go there sometime…together.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Takeba</> takes great care of the bathhouse. We should go there sometime…together.

Text.SourceString: Having short hair is awesome for beach volleyball.//Sand just slides right off. No fuss, no muss.
Text.LocalizedString: Having short hair is awesome for beach volleyball.//Sand just slides right off. No fuss, no muss.

Text.SourceString: <Italic>Man</>, shoveling snow is such a workout. My arms are gonna be sore tomorrow.
Text.LocalizedString: <Italic>Man</>, shoveling snow is such a workout. My arms are gonna be sore tomorrow.

Text.SourceString: Oh, no, no! Don't worry, I actually want to do it. It's good for me to get moving.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, no, no! Don't worry, I actually want to do it. It's good for me to get moving.

Text.SourceString: These icy sidewalks give me anxiety, I swear. I’m so afraid of slipping and falling!//Can’t take any chances when I only have two legs.
Text.LocalizedString: These icy sidewalks give me anxiety, I swear. I’m so afraid of slipping and falling!//Can’t take any chances when I only have two legs.

Text.SourceString: Please, <NPCName>Goddess</>, keep me safe out there.
Text.LocalizedString: Please, <NPCName>Goddess</>, keep me safe out there.

Text.SourceString: Can’t wait for Summer to roll around again! The beach, the sun, the sand. It’s my favorite season.
Text.LocalizedString: Can’t wait for Summer to roll around again! The beach, the sun, the sand. It’s my favorite season.

Text.SourceString: The observatory gets super chilly in Winter.//Unlike our home, it's nice and warm. I'm so glad I don't live there anymore.
Text.LocalizedString: The observatory gets super chilly in Winter.//Unlike our home, it's nice and warm. I'm so glad I don't live there anymore.

Text.SourceString: I should probably check on <NPCName>Wakuu</>, make sure he's not frozen or anything.
Text.LocalizedString: I should probably check on <NPCName>Wakuu</>, make sure he's not frozen or anything.

Text.SourceString: Ben hooked us up with this <Italic>thing</> that's supposed to ward off bad spirits.//It's like a round lamp, so who knows if it's the real deal...
Text.LocalizedString: Ben hooked us up with this <Italic>thing</> that's supposed to ward off bad spirits.//It's like a round lamp, so who knows if it's the real deal...

Text.SourceString: But just in case it actually works, I set it up in our home gym.//Bam! No more bad spirits, babe. I gotchu.
Text.LocalizedString: But just in case it actually works, I set it up in our home gym.//Bam! No more bad spirits, babe. I gotchu.

Text.SourceString: Oh, the observatory is <Italic>totally</> haunted, no doubt.//I've heard some weird noises at 2-3 AM in the morning...and trust me, that's definitely not <NPCName>Wakuu</> making those sounds.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, the observatory is <Italic>totally</> haunted, no doubt.//I've heard some weird noises at 2-3 AM in the morning...and trust me, that's definitely not <NPCName>Wakuu</> making those sounds.

Text.SourceString: I never dared to check, nope! Can't risk getting <Italic>eaten</> by a ghost.
Text.LocalizedString: I never dared to check, nope! Can't risk getting <Italic>eaten</> by a ghost.

Text.SourceString: It’s always a good idea to swim with a buddy or stay close to the lifeguard tower. I’m here to help if anything goes wrong.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s always a good idea to swim with a buddy or stay close to the lifeguard tower. I’m here to help if anything goes wrong.

Text.SourceString: What do you think of my lifeguard speech, babe? Nailed it, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: What do you think of my lifeguard speech, babe? Nailed it, huh?

Text.SourceString: If you start feelin’ dizzy, head to the Beach Shack and grab a drink.
Text.LocalizedString: If you start feelin’ dizzy, head to the Beach Shack and grab a drink.

Text.SourceString: Chill in the shade and avoid that direct sun.//<portrait=sad>I don’t want you gettin’ heatstroke or anything.
Text.LocalizedString: Chill in the shade and avoid that direct sun.//<portrait=sad>I don’t want you gettin’ heatstroke or anything.

Text.SourceString: The sunset at the beach is just unreal.//Stick around and watch it with me.
Text.LocalizedString: The sunset at the beach is just unreal.//Stick around and watch it with me.

Text.SourceString: I’ve been working on my serve lately. It’s all about that perfect balance of power and control, you know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve been working on my serve lately. It’s all about that perfect balance of power and control, you know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: After a long day at work or practice, I like to unwind with a big bowl of ramen.//<portrait=happy>The spicier, the better!
Text.LocalizedString: After a long day at work or practice, I like to unwind with a big bowl of ramen.//<portrait=happy>The spicier, the better!

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Aaliyah’s</> got this cool plane sweater, huh? I wonder if they make one with a duck or somethin’.//<portrait=determined>I’d totally rock that.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Aaliyah’s</> got this cool plane sweater, huh? I wonder if they make one with a duck or somethin’.//<portrait=determined>I’d totally rock that.

Text.SourceString: You should come join me for a workout sometime!//I could show you some of my favorite exercises, and we could keep each other motivated.
Text.LocalizedString: You should come join me for a workout sometime!//I could show you some of my favorite exercises, and we could keep each other motivated.

Text.SourceString: Yesterday morning, I did my workout at the beach, and <Italic>man</>, the sand really made things more challenging.//<portrait=determined>But hey, I got to dive right into the ocean after, so it was a pretty sweet way to start the day!
Text.LocalizedString: Yesterday morning, I did my workout at the beach, and <Italic>man</>, the sand really made things more challenging.//<portrait=determined>But hey, I got to dive right into the ocean after, so it was a pretty sweet way to start the day!

Text.SourceString: I’m loving the Tavern’s playlist.//<portrait=happy>They’ve got a perfect mix of classic hits and fresh tunes. Makes me wanna bop.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m loving the Tavern’s playlist.//<portrait=happy>They’ve got a perfect mix of classic hits and fresh tunes. Makes me wanna bop.

Text.SourceString: Where do you think they get this wine from? Our farm or something?//<portrait=blushing>’Cause it’s seriously tasty! *hic*
Text.LocalizedString: Where do you think they get this wine from? Our farm or something?//<portrait=blushing>’Cause it’s seriously tasty! *hic*

Text.SourceString: Have a seat. Let’s chill out a little!
Text.LocalizedString: Have a seat. Let’s chill out a little!

Text.SourceString: One…two…one…two…
Text.LocalizedString: One…two…one…two…

Text.SourceString: Wanna join me for a workout?
Text.LocalizedString: Wanna join me for a workout?

Text.SourceString: Heading to the hot spring? It’s that way, behind this building.
Text.LocalizedString: Heading to the hot spring? It’s that way, behind this building.

Text.SourceString: Need to eat more bananas, for sure.//Don’t want any cramps after all this!
Text.LocalizedString: Need to eat more bananas, for sure.//Don’t want any cramps after all this!

Text.SourceString: The weather is nice today.//Outdoor time, baby!
Text.LocalizedString: The weather is nice today.//Outdoor time, baby!

Text.SourceString: Took me forever to put these pants on. Do they really have to be this tight?
Text.LocalizedString: Took me forever to put these pants on. Do they really have to be this tight?

Text.SourceString: Do you know where my sweatpants are, babe?//I keep misplacing stuff. Bleh.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you know where my sweatpants are, babe?//I keep misplacing stuff. Bleh.
